data.title: PHOTO CALL: Carly Rose Sonenclar, Mario Lopez and More Attend "The X Factor" Finalist Party
data.meta_description: Carly Rose Sonenclar, the young singing actress who has been seen on Broadway in Wonderland and Les Miserables , is among the top 12 finalists for Fox TV's singing competition, "The X Factor." A party was held Nov. 5 at The Bazaar at The SLS Hotel Beverly Hills.
data.text:
Judges Simon Cowell, Demi Lovato, L.A. Reid and Britney Spears revealed the Top 12 finalists Nov. 1.

The Top 12 finalists follow:

Teens – Beatrice Miller, Arin Ray and Carly Rose Sonenclar

Young Adults – CeCe Frey, Jennel Garcia and Paige Thomas

Over 25s – Vino Alan, Jason Brock and Tate Stevens

Groups – 1432, Emblem3 and Lyric 145

On Nov. 7 at 8 PM ET, the Top 12 finalists, with the help of their mentors, took the stage once again to perform. This time it will be up to America, as well as the judges, to decide who moves forward in the competition.

On Nov. 8 at 8 PM ET, hosts Khloé Kardashian Odom and Mario Lopez will reveal the results of America’s votes as one finalist is eliminated from the competition.
